headline: Teradyne to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Results
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., July 14, 2025--Teradyne, Inc. (NASDAQ: TER) will release financial results for the second quarter 2025 on Tuesday, July 29 at 5:00 p.m. Eastern Time (ET) or later.

headline: Why Teradyne (TER) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of semiconductor testing company Teradyne (NASDAQ:TER) fell 3.1% in the morning session after a recent "Sell" rating initiation from Goldman Sachs cast a shadow over the company's growth prospects. The investment bank set a price target of $80.00, citing concerns that Teradyne is not well-positioned in the high-growth market for testing merchant GPUs (Graphics Processing Units), which are crucial for AI applications. headline: Strength Seen in Gauzy Ltd. (GAUZ): Can Its 9.4% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Gauzy Ltd. (GAUZ) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.
